-- Chavez Says Currency Controls Not Affected by Joining Mercosur
-- B y   J o s e   O r o z c o
-- 2012-07-26T02:45:02Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-07-26/chavez-says-currency-controls-not-affected-by-joining-mercosur.html
Venezuelan President  Hugo Chavez 
said the Mercosur trade bloc does not interfere with internal
policies of member countries and joining the group would not
affect currency controls in the South American country.  Chavez spoke on state television.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Jose Orozco in Caracas at 
 jorozco8@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Jonathan Roeder at 
 jroeder@bloomberg.net  